sets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c279b7f58c804756a1b85944640695abf43b45c4","tid":497321,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T04:27:23.000Z","msg":"8u + 68u aimesh開心享用中"},{"pid":"611b5de3963a56e0c6061265d1cc8683658ba9c8","tid":497321,"uid":130595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T07:09:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好老實r7000 各方都係勁少少，但實際上分別真係感受唔到<br />\n<br />\n不過個firmware 同功能方面asus真係贏到到開晒行車尾燈都見唔到<br />\n<br />\nr7000 都可以flash merlin 但係過程相對複雜好多，因為要裝過渡firmware<br />\n我都試過r7000 flash merlin 想改大d 5hz 功率,跟足方法都係改唔到 最大只係23dbm 200mw<br />\n亦有人講flash 完 wifi 無以前穩定<br />\n<br />\n反而68u stock firmware set 澳洲 已經可以25dbm 即係320mw<br />\n<br />\n如果淨係想要router 射下wifi 兩部都係穩定無問題，但係如果想要高少少既功能，我建議ac68u</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講firmware, 梗係ddwrt<br />\n<br />\nr7000 有kong's mod<br />\n<br />\nac68u 又其實可以買ac66u b1 取代, flash 個ac68u ddwrt 落去就變身68u<br />\n<br />\n自從今年年中, ddwrt 有SFE 之後, merlin 已經無左優勢"},{"pid":"3838424e79c82766f9cb3fa51b9c669bddcdedae","tid":497321,"uid":10610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T13:57:52.000Z","msg":"有無人用r7000<br />\n連左ps4<br />\n下載會得30幾mbs<br />\n上載有200幾咁"},{"pid":"a6ed4262fc2d3d99db9a13be33e2f3f4e1ad43eb","tid":497321,"uid":10329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T14:24:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人用r7000<br />\n連左ps4<br />\n下載會得30幾mbs<br />\n上載有200幾咁</blockquote><br />\n我HKBN100mb<br />\n呢兩日都買左R7000同樣有呢個情況<br />\n用Speedtest得返DL45mb UL正常<br />\n但用OFCAtest又有DL 70mb<br />\n另外wifi穿牆力應該係差過ac68u<br />\n<br />\n下個月轉nevigator 1000MB<br />\nDL speed如果得返一半會放左佢買68u"},{"pid":"651120d61124c2ce208591fda518f3f1f4f321bd","tid":497321,"uid":82970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T14:26:38.000Z","msg":"ac68u用咩firmware最好? 依家用緊merlin幾正, 咁ddwrt, tomato 同其他呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c838227a718304025f8896c5c2c582140fdfe8a0","tid":497321,